title: NFL Free Agents with Pete Prisco, AAF kickoff with Ben Kercheval (Football 2/8)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Pete Prisco to break down the upcoming free agent class for the 2019 NFL offseason. Then Ben Kercheval hops on the podcast to tell us everything we need to know about the upcoming Alliance of American Football league that will start up on Saturday, including a breakdown of the rules, rosters, teams and gambling options (because gambling is legal in Bushwood this time).
